 It is apparent that you are not only unaware of how Oregon accomplished its 
well deserved trip to the Rose Bowl, but of biblical history as well. So, it is 
our duty to inform you that David did defeat Goliath, and with only one small 
stone. 
</P>
<P>
 JOHN LEONE 
