 The two, described by authorities as gang members, were fighting over the 
suspect's wife, Francis said, but details were unclear. There were no injuries 
in the shooting outside the restaurant on Cabot Road. 
</P>
<P>
 Deputies made the arrest after stopping Smith in a car on the San Diego 
Freeway. Investigators later were searching beside the freeway for a 
.25-caliber handgun they believe he threw out of the car. KEN ELLINGWOOD 
