<HEADLINE>
<P>
GIVING AND SHARING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 As we contemplate the season of giving, I would like to remind people about an 
extraordinary organization right here in Ventura County that is all about 
giving and sharing. That organization is the Big Brother/Big Sister Program. 
</P>
<P>
 I have been a "big sister" for over 2 1/2 years and it is one of the most 
rewarding experiences of my life. Like many of you, I have been fortunate in my 
life to have a safe living environment filled with love and opportunity. Now I 
have the chance to share the things in my life that I am thankful for with 
another person. And it isn't a one-way street; my life is enriched by the time 
my "little sister" and I spend together. 
</P>
<P>
 Currently the Big Brother/Big Sister Program is recruiting new big brothers 
and sisters. There are over 100 children waiting for a big brother or sister 
here in Ventura County. 
</P>
<P>
 DONNA M. HERBERT, Ventura 
</P>
